import React from 'react';

const CricketBallIcon = () => {
  return (
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="48"
      height="48"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      className="cricket-bat-icon"
    >
      {/* Cricket Bat Handle */}
      <rect
        x="10"
        y="15"
        width="4"
        height="6"
        fill="#795548"
        stroke="#5d4037"
        strokeWidth="1"
        rx="2"
      />
      
      {/* Cricket Bat Blade */}
      <rect
        x="8"
        y="9"
        width="8"
        height="6"
        fill="#6d4c41"
        stroke="#4e342e"
        strokeWidth="1"
        rx="1.5"
      />
      
      {/* Top of the Bat */}
      <path
        d="M12 6l-2-3l2-1l2 1l-2 3z"
        fill="#3e2723"
        stroke="#2c211d"
        strokeWidth="1"
      />
    </svg>
  );
};

export default CricketBallIcon;
